  "remarks": "Explosives expert and operative for the Abdallah Azzam Brigades (AAB)\n(QDe.144). Wanted by the Saudi Arabian Government for terrorism. Physical description:\neye colour: dark; hair colour: dark; complexion: olive. Speaks Arabic. Photo available\nfor inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice.  Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
